- 0.05n = 25

So we want: P(|Y - 125| < 25)

**Using Chebyshev's Inequality:**
Chebyshev's inequality states: P(|Y - μ| ≥ kσ) ≤ 1/k²

Therefore: P(|Y - μ| < kσ) ≥ 1 - 1/k²

**Finding k:**
