- σ = √93.75 ≈ 9.682
- We need |Y - 125| < 25

So: k = 25/σ = 25/√93.75 = 25/9.682 ≈ 2.582

**Applying Chebyshev's bound:**
P(|Y - 125| < 25) ≥ 1 - 1/k²
= 1 - 1/(2.582)²
= 1 - 1/6.667
= 1 - 0.15
= 0.85

